geneVariantDescriptions.description: MYC F138S lies within the Myc box 2 of the Myc protein (PMID: 23673335). F138S has been identified in sequencing studies (PMID: 27303665, PMID: 23673335), but has not been biochemically characterized and therefore, its effect on Myc protein function is unknown (PubMed, Nov 2019).
